{"tid":1755410,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彭博宣布參加美國民主黨總統初選　揚言要挫敗特朗普","createTime":"2019-11-25T14:36:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T15:03:39.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0fc33f336b68263b3df2a486c799c323d21dc980","tid":1755410,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:36:26.000Z","msg":"彭博宣布參加美國民主黨總統初選　揚言要挫敗特朗普<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1494251-20191125.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1494251-20191125.htm&d=yZvzIFdj7oCTZXRWgogUmUYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=c01ccdb0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1494251-20191125.htm&h=80f1cbd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1494251-20191125.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國富商、紐約前市長彭博，宣布參加民主黨總統初選。<br />\n<br />\n77歲的彭博表示，參選是要擊敗總統特朗普，以及重建美國，美國人不能夠再承受特朗普的魯莽及不道德的行為多四年，特朗普威脅著美國及美國的價值觀，若果他連任成功，美國將永遠無法從損害中回復過來。"},{"pid":"6c31a71cfa421a558611e9990f5a8263764779e8","tid":1755410,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:37:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1dd246813e91bd0d9dc6920320a39c20a5e954b6","tid":1755410,"uid":264400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:40:35.000Z","msg":"Hkaa要出動了"},{"pid":"3b656a822748c4d936c3b5ef5333295ad298ddf9","tid":1755410,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:52:07.000Z","msg":"Biden收皮<br />\n要換佢上"},{"pid":"39ebf3b95881ceaf7f9f179c227d6daa9397e552","tid":1755410,"uid":148438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:53:04.000Z","msg":"77歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8224e0bff969ab994daae4d5ec47ee9bd2f9dbc5","tid":1755410,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b656a822748c4d936c3b5ef5333295